Wages data

My degree project in applied mathematics was based on the system of differential equations with delay who control the movement of a mobile plate of the MEMS model known as Comb-drive. $$ \left. \begin{aligned} \dot{x_1} & = x_2\\ \dot{x_2} & = \frac{38.8539 \times 10^{-4} (2.5-G({x_{2\tau}}-x_2))^2x_1}{(1-x_1^2)^2} - 0.7297 x_2 - x_1 + 0.05 \end{aligned} \right \rbrace. $$ Where $G \in \mathbb{R} $, $x_1$ is the position and $x_2$ is the velocity.
